{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_2774d7dd0ffeOnrt7jO6r8uvEJ","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d88b295ca001wKjuLvL6wpTQQG","parts":[{"id":"prt_d88b29d99001bwsPNjsQ644hfW","messageID":"msg_d88b295ca001wKjuLvL6wpTQQG","sessionID":"ses_2774d7dd0ffeOnrt7jO6r8uvEJ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7d8be6d84d4945c3bb4e36b0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/workspace/README.md"},"output":"<path>/workspace/README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>1: # Bitcart\n2: \n3: ![Github All Contributors](https://img.shields.io/github/all-contributors/bitcart/bitcart?style=flat-square)\n4: [![CI](https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/actions/workflows/ci.yml)\n5: ![Codecov](https://img.shields.io/codecov/c/github/bitcart/bitcart?style=flat-square)\n6: [![Python versions](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/bitcart?style=flat-square)](https://docs.bitcart.ai)\n7: \n8: Bitcart is a platform for merchants, users and developers which offers easy setup and use.\n9: \n10: ## Linked repositories\n11: \n12: Our ecosystem consists of a few packages, this is our central repository.\n13: \n14: It is recommended to propose feature requests to Bitcart ecosystem as a whole on that repository.\n15: \n16: Full list of our repositories:\n17: \n18: https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart - Bitcart Core Daemons and Merchants API\n19: \n20: https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-admin - The admin panel of Bitcart\n21: \n22: https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-store - Bitcart ready store\n23: \n24: https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-docker - Docker packaging, base for all deployment methods\n25: \n26: https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-sdk - Python library for coins connection\n27: \n28: https://github.com/bitcart/bitccl - The BitCCL scripting language for checkout flow automation\n29: \n30: https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-docs - [Bitcart documentation](https://docs.bitcart.ai)\n31: \n32: https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-site - [Bitcart official site](https://bitcart.ai)\n33: \n34: ## Docs\n35: \n36: Docs are available at https://docs.bitcart.ai or in our [docs repository](https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-docs)\n37: \n38: ## Contributing\n39: \n40: See [our contributing guidelines](https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md) for details.\n41: \n42: ## Contributors ✨\n43: \n44: Thanks goes to these wonderful people ([emoji key](https://allcontributors.org/docs/en/emoji-key)):\n45: \n46: <!-- ALL-CONTRIBUTORS-LIST:START - Do not remove or modify this section -->\n47: <!-- prettier-ignore-start -->\n48: <!-- markdownlint-disable -->\n49: <table>\n50:   <tbody>\n51:     <tr>\n52:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/MrNaif2018\"><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/39452697?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"MrNaif2018\"/><br /><sub><b>MrNaif2018</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"#maintenance-MrNaif2018\" title=\"Maintenance\">🚧</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=MrNaif2018\" title=\"Code\">💻</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=MrNaif2018\" title=\"Documentation\">📖</a> <a href=\"#design-MrNaif2018\" title=\"Design\">🎨</a></td>\n53:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/tomasmor42\"><img src=\"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/42064734?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"tomasmor42\"/><br /><sub><b>tomasmor42</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=tomasmor42\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n54:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/yagicandegirmenci\"><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/62724709?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Yağız Değirmenci\"/><br /><sub><b>Yağız Değirmenci</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=yagicandegirmenci\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n55:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/xiaoxianma\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/3086064?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Weidong Sun\"/><br /><sub><b>Weidong Sun</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=xiaoxianma\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n56:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/kartecianos\"><img src=\"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/43797783?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"kartecianos\"/><br /><sub><b>kartecianos</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=kartecianos\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n57:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/arynn-gupta\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/61794851?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"CYBORG\"/><br /><sub><b>CYBORG</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"#design-arynn-gupta\" title=\"Design\">🎨</a></td>\n58:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/SakshamSingh-v2\"><img src=\"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/55451173?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Saksham Singh\"/><br /><sub><b>Saksham Singh</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"#design-SakshamSingh-v2\" title=\"Design\">🎨</a></td>\n59:     </tr>\n60:     <tr>\n61:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/orestischaral\"><img src=\"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/33599092?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Orestis Charalampakos\"/><br /><sub><b>Orestis Charalampakos</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"#design-orestischaral\" title=\"Design\">🎨</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=orestischaral\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n62:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"http://tobyase.de/\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/6002167?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"TobyAsE\"/><br /><sub><b>TobyAsE</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=TobyAsE\" title=\"Code\">💻</a> <a href=\"#design-TobyAsE\" title=\"Design\">🎨</a></td>\n63:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Shadman-Ahmed-Chowdhury\"><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/46925021?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Shadman Ahmed\"/><br /><sub><b>Shadman Ahmed</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"#design-Shadman-Ahmed-Chowdhury\" title=\"Design\">🎨</a></td>\n64:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/KarolTrzeszczkowski\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/11697819?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Karol Trzeszczkowski\"/><br /><sub><b>Karol Trzeszczkowski</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=KarolTrzeszczkowski\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n65:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/MaximeKoitsalu\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8655862?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Maxime Koitsalu\"/><br /><sub><b>Maxime Koitsalu</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=MaximeKoitsalu\" title=\"Code\">💻</a> <a href=\"#design-MaximeKoitsalu\" title=\"Design\">🎨</a></td>\n66:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://git.io/JuT7Z\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/88304238?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Shubham-Singh-Rajput\"/><br /><sub><b>Shubham-Singh-Rajput</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"#translation-shubham-singh-748\" title=\"Translation\">🌍</a></td>\n67:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Xaconi\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1944438?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Nicolás Giacconi\"/><br /><sub><b>Nicolás Giacconi</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=Xaconi\" title=\"Code\">💻</a> <a href=\"#design-Xaconi\" title=\"Design\">🎨</a></td>\n68:     </tr>\n69:     <tr>\n70:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/leovoon\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16155802?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"leovoon\"/><br /><sub><b>leovoon</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=leovoon\" title=\"Code\">💻</a> <a href=\"#design-leovoon\" title=\"Design\">🎨</a> <a href=\"#a11y-leovoon\" title=\"Accessibility\">️️️️♿️</a></td>\n71:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/mustaphanezzari\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4595534?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Mustapha Nezzari\"/><br /><sub><b>Mustapha Nezzari</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"#translation-MawsFr\" title=\"Translation\">🌍</a></td>\n72:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/surfer190\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3285222?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"surfer190\"/><br /><sub><b>surfer190</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=surfer190\" title=\"Documentation\">📖</a></td>\n73:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/restyler\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/775507?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"restyler\"/><br /><sub><b>restyler</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=restyler\" title=\"Documentation\">📖</a></td>\n74:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://www.groestlcoin.org/\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/11212268?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"gruve-p\"/><br /><sub><b>gruve-p</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=gruve-p\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n75:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/g00g1\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/91201021?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"g00g1\"/><br /><sub><b>g00g1</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=g00g1\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n76:       <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Ravaan21\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/48627542?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"RAVAAN\"/><br /><sub><b>RAVAAN</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"#security-Ravaan21\" title=\"Security\">🛡️</a></td>\n77:     </tr>\n78:   </tbody>\n79: </table>\n80: \n81: <!-- markdownlint-restore -->\n82: <!-- prettier-ignore-end -->\n83: \n84: <!-- ALL-CONTRIBUTORS-LIST:END -->\n85: \n86: This project follows the [all-contributors](https://github.com/all-contributors/all-contributors) specification. Contributions of any kind welcome!\n87: \n88: ## Copyright and License\n89: \n90: Copyright (C) 2019 MrNaif2018\n91: \n92: Licensed under the [MIT license](LICENSE)\n\n(End of file - total 92 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Bitcart\n\n![Github All Contributors](https://img.shields.io/github/all-contributors/bitcart/bitcart?style=flat-square)\n[![CI](https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/actions/workflows/ci.yml)\n![Codecov](https://img.shields.io/codecov/c/github/bitcart/bitcart?style=flat-square)\n[![Python versions](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/bitcart?style=flat-square)](https://docs.bitcart.ai)\n\nBitcart is a platform for merchants, users and developers which offers easy setup and use.\n\n## Linked repositories\n\nOur ecosystem consists of a few packages, this is our central repository.\n\nIt is recommended to propose feature requests to Bitcart ecosystem as a whole on that repository.\n\nFull list of our repositories:\n\nhttps://github.com/bitcart/bitcart - Bitcart Core Daemons and Merchants API\n\nhttps://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-admin - The admin panel of Bitcart","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"README.md","time":{"start":1776114900667,"end":1776114900679}}}]}
